Description:
    This will install a Jenkinsfile to build two Dockerfile pods and push then to Kubernetes.

Example:
    rails generate ci_k8s:install

    This will create:
        # Jekinsfile
        # Dockerfile
        # Dockerfile.test
        # database.yml.prod
        # database.yml.test
        # k8s/<app_name>_deployment.yaml
        # k8s/<app_name>_service.yaml
        # k8s/<app_name>_tests_job.yaml
        # k8s/<app_name>_setup_job.yaml
